{"id": "1384734822706057228", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "512881362223759360", "author_name": "x013318908", "author_bot": false, "content": "日本版、オート戦闘あるのってどうなの？スレスパにも無いけど。\nその代わり2倍速スイッチが無い？（その後で出てきました）", "timestamp": "2025-06-18T03:21:48.862000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-06-18T06:27:22.647000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
