{"id": "1384904766525542451", "channel_id": "1300659436804640788", "type": 0, "author_id": "746653501630840920", "author_name": "2dm14_", "author_bot": false, "content": "今ポイズンを軸にパーティーを組んでいるのですが、今後集めたほうがいいキャラなどはいますか？メルトダウンを軸にパーティーを組みたいと思っています。アドバイスお願いします。", "timestamp": "2025-06-18T14:37:06.626000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1384904766244782161", "filename": "2025-06-18_232905.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2435817, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1300659436804640788/1384904766244782161/2025-06-18_232905.png?ex=6a36a592&is=6a355412&hm=2ff9adf78cd5207ae3bc6dc900a203f90ad352a7a6830200344151cfeeca3744&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
